    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/9135c6e2061170a62f809855d3470326.poster.avif?t=1764332709\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/9135c6e2061170a62f809855d3470326.webm?t=1764332709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/9135c6e2061170a62f809855d3470326.mp4?t=1764332709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>起锚，上膛，大开杀戒！</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>精心手绘，激烈战斗</strong>：体验让人上气不接下气的史诗级对战，感受众多第一人称射击经典大作的身影！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>军火齐备，武器致命</strong>：善用Captain Wayne的各种究极杀伤武器，神挡杀神，佛挡杀佛！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>八个地点，宏大场景</strong>：探索8个超大区域，克服各种挑战和危险，走遍整个虎鲸岛！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>一半游戏，一半卡通</strong>： 加入战役模式，<strong>欣赏海量卡通过场动画</strong>，一边享受冒险，一边探索Captain精彩绝伦的故事。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>劲爆原声，点燃全场</strong>：体验充满浩劫风和侵略感的高能原声带！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>无尽战斗，考验实力</strong>：加入无尽模式，一次次突破个人记录，在四面八方涌来的敌群中，你能存活多久？能否拿到金牌？<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/e8529870a5b4c3f16f4690f4cf2ea256.poster.avif?t=1764332709\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/e8529870a5b4c3f16f4690f4cf2ea256.webm?t=1764332709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/e8529870a5b4c3f16f4690f4cf2ea256.mp4?t=1764332709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/5fd72ac4a39b43c61b49f372ce1402c5.avif?t=1764332709\" width=482 height=545 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong></strong><br><br><br><strong>化身成为Captain！！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >硬汉风里透出一点火辣的粉红，不离齿间的雪茄烟雾缭绕，渴了饿了就吃条鱼——<strong>Captain Wayne</strong>就是这样一位充满魅力的人物！他立志要羞辱全世界所有有钱的混蛋，还要将他们的财富洗劫一空。“挡我者死！”就是他的座右铭。<br><br>在与传奇<strong>尖牙饮血大白鲸</strong>的血腥搏斗中，Captain Wayne失去了一条胳膊。不过没关系——他将一直陪伴自己的霰弹枪“<strong>轰天罡</strong>”装在断臂上当成义肢，以后连掏枪都省了！坐着他的<strong>海盐号</strong>，带着手架火炮，Captain Wayne驶遍了七个半大洋。<br><br>可叹天有不测风云，Wayne意外遭到了一群邪恶佣兵的袭击，不仅搁浅在了<strong>虎鲸岛</strong>上，连船都被敌人偷走了！遭遇如此变故，Captain自然掏出了他的看家绝活儿：<strong>彻底消灭每一个需要负责的人。</strong><br><br><br><strong></strong><br><br><br>带着双管霰弹枪做成的义肢，无穷无尽的炸药，还有“爷就是这么拽”的态度，你必须找到<strong>Killer Whales</strong>，近身报私仇。不过，Killer Whales可是七个半大洋上最臭名昭著、最残忍的佣兵帮派！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>化身Captain，大杀四方，你有这个实力吗？</strong> 来试试吧！<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/ebe46df394016c6d88319b079e143d6d.poster.avif?t=1764332709\" width=616 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/ebe46df394016c6d88319b079e143d6d.webm?t=1764332709\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2319790/extras/ebe46df394016c6d88319b079e143d6d.mp4?t=1764332709\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><strong></strong><br><br><strong></strong><br><br><br><strong>释放Wayne的狂怒！！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用<strong>双管霰弹枪手炮</strong>将敌人轰成齑粉，发射<strong>钩链指，</strong>出其不意手撕敌人。四面楚歌？没关系，扔一瓶<strong>爆炸性的团灭酒</strong>，或者干脆雷神附体，伸手发动<strong>雷霆之力</strong>。<strong>当然，直接徒手硬刚，将敌人锤成肉酱，也是不错的选择！</strong><br><br><br><strong></strong><br><strong>还等什么？！</strong> 吉时已到，劫富济悍将，送Killer Whales的那群王八蛋上路吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
